Soon after he said everything here, he went and did it.
A quick summary of the seven most important conclusions of the Lost Interview:
About how he learned to run a business:
"All my life in business, I've been asked, 'Why are you doing this?' and the answer you always get is, 'Oh, that's just the way it's done.'
Nobody knows why they do what they do, nobody thinks about business very deeply.
